{"tid":103200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普指中日操控匯率 日方稱指責毫無道理","createTime":"2017-02-01T07:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T09:09:56.000Z","uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89f7bcd44f4a1dde0fde0c2c51d3665ff3c5ce25","tid":103200,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普批評中國和日本操控匯率，令貨幣貶值。<br />\n<br />\n特朗朗說，中國正在操控匯率，日本過去一段時間亦有這樣做。特朗普又不點名批評，其他一些國家亦有操控匯率。<br />\n<br />\n分析相信，他說的是歐洲央行。<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣官房長官菅義偉說，有關指責毫無道理，日方的措施是為了穩定物價，不是故意誘導日元貶值。<br />\n<br />\n日本央行總裁黑田東彥說，國際貨幣基金組織最近並無指人民幣幣值被低估，因此不能將中國視為匯率操縱國。"},{"pid":"cfd6a9f5310c7480a16e7fb7c473532322851942","tid":103200,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"特朗普屌均全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdc99721d22fcf8d5678b79dba868c031b4aff7","tid":103200,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"日本:「屌你, 你搞中國算啦, 做乜拖埋我落水」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4307c5d02591df2bfd7d1a22d685fd76c72699","tid":103200,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"全世界都迫害緊美國"},{"pid":"f7d3158d11abffbaa6811d074eb292e5973f6889","tid":103200,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本:「屌你, 你搞中國算啦, 做乜拖埋我落水」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辦嘢姐，唔拖埋日本點顯得大公無私？"},{"pid":"509a1e6b8dbafb4230fed13831f2a8d313413ae1","tid":103200,"uid":19267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"安倍經濟學實際上冇乜用 想操控都冇得操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da6b3726ab16b0a0601b7efa336933b11d43da0","tid":103200,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:43:49.000Z","